---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts'
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Hi! I'm Nikita.</h1>

      I'm a Software Engineer based in Prague, Czech Republic 🇨🇿.

      <ul>
        <li>
          I develop <a
            href='https://www.saboit.de/references/audi-dpa'
            target='_blank'>complex and high-performance user interfaces</a
          > ⚡ using modern tools like React ⚛️ and WebGL.
        </li>
        <li>
          I enjoy solving problems with software and take a practical approach
          to my work. My pet projects include a Teams lunch bot, a Telegram news
          bot, a personal finance app, and a streaming app.
        </li>
        <li>
          In the past, I worked with the iOS platform using Swift and
          Objective-C and <a
            href='https://www.saboit.de/blog/lidar-data-in-arkit-3-5'
            target='_blank'>explored</a
          > the early versions of ARKit.
        </li>
        <li>
          I enjoy working with 3D graphics and VR, making <a
            href='https://hacknick.itch.io/christmas-mini-game'
            target='_blank'>small games</a
          > and occasionally to participate in <a
            href='https://ldjam.com/events/ludum-dare/53/delirium-and-deliverance'
            target='_blank'>game jams</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          I like electronic music and have created <a
            href='https://soundcloud.com/pulse-infestation'
            target='_blank'>several tracks</a
          > 🎵 and I am learning to play the piano 🎹
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Checkout my blog where I share my knowledge about building complex 3D
        systems for the web and other interesting stuff.
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
